3: You know it full well. Even the power of Tenebrion is under my control.
You depend on me to fend against the corruption.
I, am the only one fit for this body.
I did it with my will and fought so from the beginning till now.
That's how it was, how it is, and how it will be.
I'll never be strayed by anything, I'll only follow my own will. I have not lost yet!
Words do nothing! Look at you! Only absolute power can protect you from all that stands in your way.
Give me your body, then perish—
